**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/.terraform.tfstate.lock.info
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.backup
**/terraform.tfvars
**/crash.log
my-cluster/
.oc-mirror.log
.image-built
